No.1/34/1/2014-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 4th June, 2014
The undersigned is directed to say that consequent upon the demise of Shri
Gopinathrao Munde, Minister of Rural Development; Minister of Panchayati Raj; and Minister
of Drinking Water and Sanitation on the 3rd June, 2014, Shri Nitin Jairam Gadkari assumed the
additional charge of the office of the Minister of Rural Development; Minister of Panchayati Raj;
and Minister of Drinking Water and Sanitation. He will continue to hold the charge of the office
of the Minister of Road Transport and Highways; and Minister of Shipping.
(K.L. Sharma)
for Cabinet Secretary
Tele: 23015802
To
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded for information to:
Secretary to the President.
Secretary to the Vice-President.
Principal Secretary to the Prime Minister.
(K.L. Sharma)
Joint Secretary (Cabinet)
Copy forwarded to:
(i)
all Secretaries to the Govt. of India, Chairman, Railway Board, Accounts Officer,
Pay & Accounts Office, Cabinet Affairs, for information.
(ii)
all Ministries/Departments of the Govt. of India, Lok Sabha Secretariat
(Distribution Branch), Rajya Sabha Secretariat (Distribution Branch),
Establishment Officer, Department of Personnel & Training, Ministry of External
Affairs (Protocol Division), Principal Director General (M&C), PIB, Section Officer,
NGO Section, Prime Minister's Office, for information.
(K.L. Sharma)
Joint Secretary (Cabinet)
*BK*
425 Copies.
